256
00:13:25,806 --> 00:13:29,242
(Kuroiwa) 《That's Manami-san's power》

257
00:13:29,309 --> 00:13:32,746
📱〔Maiho Ryu-kun (Manami) is really strong on the edge of the ring→

258
00:13:32,812 --> 00:13:34,681
That's not the way to fall.]

