>> Huh?

326
00:17:34,921 --> 00:17:39,426
(Manami) I absolutely don't want anyone to die.

327
00:17:44,931 --> 00:17:47,367
>> I won't do anything that Manami doesn't like.

328
00:17:47,434 --> 00:17:48,935
